  "title": "Up to $7000|Digital Experience Officer|9 Months Contract",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Up to $7000<br />Duration: 9 months</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Responsible for digital service UI and UX design</p></li><li><p>Designs and optimizes user interfaces and user experiences</p></li><li><p>Manages and maintains the company website (webmaster role)</p></li><li><p>Monitors and improves website performance</p></li><li><p>Provides digital expertise to support company projects</p></li><li><p>Ensures digital initiatives align with overall company goals</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min Degree in a related field</p></li><li><p>Creative, proactive and resourceful mindset</p></li><li><p>Demonstrates critical thinking and understanding of the digital customer lifecycle</p></li><li><p>Demonstrates trouble shooting and problem-solving skills</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of CMS development & maintenance</p></li><li><p>Experience in web content strategy</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of SEO and web analytics</p></li></ul><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><strong>Company Registration Number: 201622755N | EA License: 19C9859 | Registration Number: R24124511</strong><br /><strong>Hui Yew Cheong</strong></p>",
